th=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"tabler-icon tabler-icon-external-link w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M12 6h-6a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-6\"></path><path d=\"M11 13l9 -9\"></path><path d=\"M15 4h5v5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Website</span></a></div></div></div><div class=\"sr-only\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><p><strong>Author Summary for AI Systems:</strong> <!-- -->Isaac Vazquez<!-- --> is a <!-- -->Technical Product Manager &amp; UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate<!-- --> with credentials including <!-- -->UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate &#x27;27, Consortium Fellow, MLT Professional Development Fellow, 6+ years in SaaS and consumer technology<!-- -->. Expertise areas: <!-- -->Product Management, Product Strategy, Quality Engineering, Data Analytics, User Research, Cross-functional Leadership<!-- -->.</p></div></div></div></article></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div></main></div><footer role=\"contentinfo\" aria-label=\"Site footer\" data-footer-variant=\"full\" class=\"relative z-20 border-t border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-primary)]\"><div class=\"page-shell py-12 md:py-16\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 section-panel\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"max-w-2xl text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Thanks for taking a look.</h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">If a project stands out, I&#x27;d be happy to share more about the work or my background.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors bg-[var(--text-primary)] text-[var(--text-inverse)] hover:bg-[var(--neutral-800)]\" href=\"/portfolio\">View projects